  "description": "bodyFreq=62Hz (B♭ — harmonically neutral territory, neither A nor C). Mod wheel sweeps from even harmonic world (÷2, ÷4 — safe, warm) toward odd alien world (÷3, ÷5 — Oskar Sala, serpent tones). The macro CHARACTER controls this transition directly. At CHARACTER=0: pure even stack. At CHARACTER=1.0: full Sala territory. This is the spectrum of the instrument itself — from familiar to uncanny.",
